distribution form is JN (mlf-L, 1) and we proceed by
successively drawing from the normal distribution
with mean the current draw 1-L and variance one. Then,
the following steps simulate draws from the target distributions of interest (Robert and Casella, 1999). Step
1: generate a starting value 1-L = f-L 1 • Step 2: generate
