(-0.75, -1, 1).
The sample was obtained in less than a minute of real
time. Fig. 8 presents plots of the histograms for p generated from the experiment. The distribution is centred
close to the given parameter value ( -0.75) and is approximately normal. Experiments with different start
values generated almost identical distributions and
we conclude that the RW-Gibbs sequence produces
robust estimates of the SAR model parameters.
